WEBVTT

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:02.950
Hey, good morning family! I'm excited to

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:05.390
be with you all again today. I am going to

00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:08.150
do another 'Pray with Me'video to motivate

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:10.910
yourself to pray. I'll be

00:00:10.920 --> 00:00:12.709
praying in English and I'll be praying

00:00:12.719 --> 00:00:15.710
in tongues. I

00:00:15.720 --> 00:00:18.070
believe corporate prayer is important in

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:20.429
these last days, even more than ever

00:00:20.439 --> 00:00:23.109
before. Now is the

00:00:23.119 --> 00:00:26.830
time we need to pray as a body.

00:00:26.840 --> 00:00:29.109
I believe as we join together in

00:00:29.119 --> 00:00:31.429
this video, there will be many of you

00:00:31.439 --> 00:00:33.389
praying for unsaved loved ones

00:00:33.389 --> 00:00:33.399
and

00:00:33.399 --> 00:00:36.630
the nation. Whatever is on

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:39.590
your heart, let's just pray together.

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:41.430
I'll be leading the prayer by myself;

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:44.110
I'm not going to do it with Lynn

00:00:44.110 --> 00:00:44.120
Hammond

00:00:44.120 --> 00:00:46.189
in

00:00:46.189 --> 00:00:46.199
a

00:00:46.199 --> 00:00:47.950
split

00:00:47.960 --> 00:00:49.590
screen. I'm just going

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:52.189
to do it how I

00:00:52.199 --> 00:00:54.349
pray every day by myself

00:00:54.349 --> 00:00:54.359
and

00:00:54.359 --> 00:00:55.830
seek the Lord. I'm

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:58.270
letting you into my prayer time and

00:00:58.270 --> 00:00:58.280
we

00:00:58.280 --> 00:00:59.470
are

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:01.389
just going to pray and

00:01:01.399 --> 00:01:03.270
seek the Father to see

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:06.149
what He has for us. I hope

00:01:06.159 --> 00:01:07.950
this helps you jump into the river in

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:10.590
your own personal prayer life.

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:12.070
I'm not saying I'm the greatest

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:14.550
prayer warrior, but the

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:16.469
Lord told me to do it, so I'm jumping

00:01:16.469 --> 00:01:16.479
into

00:01:16.479 --> 00:01:19.070
this river and let's

00:01:19.080 --> 00:01:21.789
see where it takes us.

00:01:21.789 --> 00:01:21.799
I

00:01:21.799 --> 00:01:23.510
always start out by singing a

00:01:23.520 --> 00:01:26.190
song to the Father. I enter His

00:01:26.190 --> 00:01:26.200
courts

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:28.069
with thanksgiving and praise, and

00:01:28.079 --> 00:01:29.350
that's what we're going to

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:31.749
do right now. Father, we just want

00:01:31.759 --> 00:01:33.510
to say thank

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:37.149
you for all that You've done and all

00:01:37.159 --> 00:01:40.469
that You're going to do. Lord, we worship

00:01:40.479 --> 00:01:42.350
You and thank You for this day. We

00:01:42.360 --> 00:01:44.030
thank You, Father, for a new day that

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:47.350
You've given us. This is the day

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:49.510
that the Lord has made, and we will

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:52.270
rejoice and be glad in it. Father, I

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:54.230
just want to say thank You for the

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:56.870
air that I breathe, for the food that we

00:01:56.880 --> 00:01:58.990
eat today, and for all that You've

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:01.310
provided. As

00:02:01.310 --> 00:02:01.320
we start

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:04.469
a new month,

00:02:04.479 --> 00:02:06.590
I thank You that we're getting

00:02:06.600 --> 00:02:09.389
ready for September and

00:02:09.399 --> 00:02:11.510
that You've provided for all the

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:13.710
bills for the month of September for

00:02:13.720 --> 00:02:15.990
every household represented here. Whether

00:02:15.990 --> 00:02:16.000
it is

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.550
electric, water,

00:02:18.560 --> 00:02:21.710
gas, phones, or car payments,

00:02:21.720 --> 00:02:23.710
whatever they have need of, Father,

00:02:23.720 --> 00:02:26.190
You've provided. I thank You, Father, that

00:02:26.200 --> 00:02:28.990
You are the great provider, the great

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:30.710
Jehovah.

00:02:30.710 --> 00:02:30.720
I

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:32.030
want to give You

00:02:32.040 --> 00:02:34.270
praise and glory. I'm

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:35.949
just going to sing You a song, Father, and

00:02:35.959 --> 00:02:37.390
I thank

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:39.790
You that You said You inhabit the

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:42.509
praises of Your people.

00:02:42.519 --> 00:02:44.710
We

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:46.790
give You praise and

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:48.670
we want to worship You today, Father.

00:02:48.680 --> 00:02:51.550
We honor You and thank You, Lord, that

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:54.869
You're so real to us and that there is a

00:02:54.879 --> 00:02:57.270
heavy presence of Your Spirit on

00:02:57.280 --> 00:03:00.390
us today.

00:03:00.390 --> 00:03:00.400
We

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:03.070
invite You

00:03:03.070 --> 00:03:03.080
into

00:03:03.080 --> 00:03:05.350
this day, into our homes, our jobs,

00:03:05.350 --> 00:03:05.360
and our workplaces.

00:03:05.360 --> 00:03:07.990
Holy Spirit,

00:03:07.990 --> 00:03:08.000
I

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:10.430
thank

00:03:10.430 --> 00:03:10.440
You

00:03:10.440 --> 00:03:11.910
that You're going

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:13.949
with our children to school today

00:03:13.949 --> 00:03:13.959
and

00:03:13.959 --> 00:03:16.309
that You protect them.

00:03:16.319 --> 00:03:18.589
No weapon formed against them

00:03:18.589 --> 00:03:18.599
shall

00:03:18.599 --> 00:03:22.110
prosper. I plead the blood over our

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:26.430
children; no weapon and no

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:28.750
devil in hell can come nigh

00:03:28.750 --> 00:03:28.760
them.

00:03:28.760 --> 00:03:31.789
Not one hair on their

00:03:31.789 --> 00:03:31.799
heads

00:03:31.799 --> 00:03:33.949
will be touched by any kind of

00:03:33.959 --> 00:03:37.110
demonic attack. I thank

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:39.229
You, Lord, that You are protecting

00:03:39.239 --> 00:03:41.509
them and that You send Your angels

00:03:43.110 --> 00:03:43.120
to

00:03:45.080 --> 00:03:46.750
bear us up in their

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:49.110
hands lest we dash our foot against a

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:51.990
stone. I thank You for Psalm 23 and

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:54.550
Psalm

00:03:54.560 --> 00:03:57.869
91. I give You praise and glory. Father,

00:03:57.879 --> 00:04:01.869
we say: fill my cup,

00:04:01.879 --> 00:04:04.780
Lord, I lift it up.

00:04:05.959 --> 00:04:10.429
Lord, come and

00:04:10.439 --> 00:04:17.390
quench

00:04:53.800 --> 00:05:00.749
this thirsting of my soul.

00:05:00.759 --> 00:05:03.110
Bread of

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:10.469
Heaven, feed me till I want no

00:05:10.479 --> 00:05:21.189
more. Fill my cup, fill it up and make me

00:05:21.199 --> 00:05:26.670
whole. It is

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:29.980
Jesus.

00:05:48.039 --> 00:05:52.029
We worship

00:05:52.039 --> 00:05:55.990
You, Holy

00:05:56.000 --> 00:06:00.830
Spirit. You are welcome

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:04.150
in this

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:06.480
place. Omnipotent

00:06:06.480 --> 00:06:06.490
Father

00:06:06.490 --> 00:06:08.070
of mercy

00:06:08.070 --> 00:06:08.080
and

00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:11.950
grace, Thou

00:06:11.950 --> 00:06:11.960
art

00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:14.150
welcome

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:17.670
in this

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:20.270
place.

00:07:24.960 --> 00:07:29.749
Jesus is coming

00:07:29.759 --> 00:07:36.469
soon, morning or night or noon. Many will

00:07:36.479 --> 00:07:41.670
meet their doom; trumpets will

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:48.149
surely sound. All of the dead shall rise,

00:07:48.159 --> 00:07:54.670
righteous meet in the sky, going where no

00:07:54.680 --> 00:08:05.670
one dies, Heavenward bound.

00:08:53.680 --> 00:09:00.870
Lord, You're coming so soon.

00:09:05.279 --> 00:09:10.030
Lord,

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:30.630
we're so thirsty

00:09:30.630 --> 00:09:30.640
and

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:33.790
we need a fresh touch

00:09:33.800 --> 00:09:38.630
today. Come and

00:09:38.640 --> 00:09:44.870
quench this thirsting of my

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:49.069
soul. Bread of

00:09:49.079 --> 00:09:55.509
Heaven, feed me till I want no

00:09:55.519 --> 00:09:57.910
more. Fill my

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:04.150
cup, fill it up and make me

00:10:04.160 --> 00:10:07.670
whole.

00:10:32.079 --> 00:10:34.870
Amazing

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:41.269
Grace, how sweet the

00:10:41.279 --> 00:10:45.269
sound that saved

00:10:45.269 --> 00:10:45.279
a wretch

00:10:45.279 --> 00:10:47.670
like

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:35.629
me. I

00:11:35.639 --> 00:11:38.629
once was

00:11:38.639 --> 00:11:44.030
lost, but now I'm

00:11:44.040 --> 00:11:46.790
found, was

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:51.040
blind but now I

00:11:56.560 --> 00:12:00.990
see. Through many

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:05.550
dangers, toils, and

00:12:05.560 --> 00:12:09.470
snares, I have

00:12:09.480 --> 00:12:13.310
already

00:12:13.310 --> 00:12:13.320
come.

00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:15.990
'Tis

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:18.030
grace that

00:12:18.040 --> 00:12:23.110
brought me safe this

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:28.150
far, and

00:12:28.160 --> 00:12:30.750
grace will lead

00:12:30.750 --> 00:12:30.760
me home.

00:12:30.760 --> 00:12:31.790
When

00:12:31.800 --> 00:12:36.230
we've been there

00:12:36.230 --> 00:12:36.240
ten

00:12:36.240 --> 00:12:39.310
thousand

00:12:39.320 --> 00:12:41.949
years, bright

00:12:41.959 --> 00:12:47.870
shining as the

00:12:47.880 --> 00:12:52.949
sun, we've

00:12:52.949 --> 00:12:52.959
no

00:12:52.959 --> 00:12:55.670
less

00:12:55.680 --> 00:13:06.790
days to sing God's praise than when

00:13:06.790 --> 00:13:06.800
we first begun.

00:13:06.800 --> 00:13:10.750
Thank You,

00:13:10.760 --> 00:13:14.310
Father, that even when we

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:16.550
mess up the words, You still inhabit

00:13:16.560 --> 00:13:19.310
the praises of Your

00:13:19.320 --> 00:13:21.590
people because it's from our

00:13:21.590 --> 00:13:21.600
hearts.

00:13:21.600 --> 00:13:24.269
Father, we thank You that

00:13:24.279 --> 00:13:27.189
if we abide in You

00:13:27.189 --> 00:13:27.199
and Your

00:13:27.199 --> 00:13:28.949
words abide in us, we shall ask what

00:13:28.949 --> 00:13:28.959
we

00:13:28.959 --> 00:13:33.310
will. We lift up all the

00:13:33.320 --> 00:13:38.550
needs of the people

00:13:38.560 --> 00:13:41.269
today. If we make much of the blood,

00:13:41.279 --> 00:13:44.470
the blood makes much of us.

00:13:50.320 --> 00:13:55.990
What can wash away my

00:13:56.000 --> 00:14:00.390
sin? Nothing but the blood of

00:14:15.399 --> 00:14:17.269
Jesus.

00:14:17.279 --> 00:14:19.749
Oh,

00:14:19.759 --> 00:14:22.990
precious is the

00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:31.670
flow that makes me white as

00:14:31.670 --> 00:14:31.680
snow;

00:14:31.680 --> 00:14:35.790
no

00:14:35.800 --> 00:14:39.189
other fount I

00:14:39.199 --> 00:14:42.629
know, nothing but the

00:14:42.639 --> 00:14:51.389
blood of

00:14:51.399 --> 00:14:57.069
Jesus. The

00:14:57.079 --> 00:15:02.189
blood that gives me strength

00:15:02.199 --> 00:15:06.310
from day to

00:15:06.320 --> 00:15:09.990
day will

00:15:10.000 --> 00:15:12.710
never

00:15:12.720 --> 00:15:16.269
lose its

00:15:16.279 --> 00:15:19.870
power, for it

00:15:19.880 --> 00:15:24.110
reaches to the

00:15:24.120 --> 00:15:29.150
highest mountain

00:15:29.160 --> 00:15:31.470
and

00:16:16.839 --> 00:16:20.870
flows to the

00:16:20.880 --> 00:16:24.470
lowest

00:16:24.480 --> 00:16:29.870
valley.

00:16:50.240 --> 00:16:55.230
Glory

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:07.630
to the

00:17:07.640 --> 00:17:08.710
Lamb!

00:17:28.960 --> 00:17:30.940
You are

00:17:34.120 --> 00:17:39.029
glorious and worthy to be

00:17:39.039 --> 00:17:41.789
praised. You're the

00:17:41.799 --> 00:17:43.909
Lamb

00:17:43.919 --> 00:17:48.950
upon the

00:17:48.960 --> 00:17:51.549
throne, and

00:17:51.559 --> 00:17:53.150
unto

00:17:53.160 --> 00:17:57.430
You, we lift our voice

00:17:57.430 --> 00:17:57.440
in

00:17:57.440 --> 00:18:00.669
praise.

00:18:20.360 --> 00:18:25.390
Father, we thank You

00:18:25.400 --> 00:18:27.350
for Your hand on this

00:18:27.360 --> 00:18:31.990
house. We worship You

00:18:31.990 --> 00:18:32.000
and

00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:35.029
give You glory

00:18:35.039 --> 00:18:39.270
right now in

00:18:39.270 --> 00:18:39.280
Jesus'name.

00:18:39.280 --> 00:18:43.630
Holy Spirit, we invite You now. What

00:18:43.640 --> 00:18:47.510
is on Your heart for us to pray for today?

00:19:20.720 --> 00:19:24.470
We yield ourselves over to the

00:19:24.480 --> 00:19:27.270
Holy

00:19:27.280 --> 00:19:29.950
Spirit and thank You that You become

00:19:29.960 --> 00:19:31.750
so real to us.

00:19:36.799 --> 00:19:40.390
There are so many needs and things pressing that seem overwhelming, but we thank You, Lord, that You are

00:19:46.600 --> 00:19:48.750
the peace in the midst of

00:19:48.760 --> 00:19:50.669
the storm.

00:19:55.480 --> 00:19:59.149
You say, 'Peace, be

00:19:59.149 --> 00:19:59.159
still,'to

00:19:59.159 --> 00:20:01.070
all

00:20:01.080 --> 00:20:04.750
storms. We call peace to every storm

00:20:04.750 --> 00:20:04.760
in

00:20:04.760 --> 00:20:07.390
the lives of every individual

00:20:07.400 --> 00:20:08.630
here

00:20:08.640 --> 00:20:11.710
today,

00:20:11.710 --> 00:20:11.720
in

00:20:11.720 --> 00:20:14.029
marriages

00:20:14.029 --> 00:20:14.039
and

00:20:14.039 --> 00:20:15.430
for

00:20:15.440 --> 00:20:19.230
children.

00:20:19.240 --> 00:20:22.390
We take authority over you, Satan,

00:20:22.400 --> 00:20:25.630
and we tell you: thus far and no further!

00:20:25.640 --> 00:20:29.990
Get your hands off of God's property.

00:20:30.000 --> 00:20:32.270
We call those in the storm of life

00:20:32.280 --> 00:20:35.029
healed, whole, and

00:20:35.039 --> 00:20:40.190
well in Jesus'name. You are the

00:20:40.200 --> 00:20:44.110
great storm

00:20:44.120 --> 00:20:47.549
peacemaker; You spoke to the

00:20:47.559 --> 00:20:53.029
waves and said, 'Peace, be

00:20:53.029 --> 00:20:53.039
still.'We

00:20:53.039 --> 00:20:55.909
thank You, Lord, that You're the

00:20:55.919 --> 00:20:56.950
mighty

00:20:56.960 --> 00:21:00.990
one, the Creator of

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:03.909
everything. You created us even in our

00:21:03.909 --> 00:21:03.919
mothers'wombs.

00:21:03.919 --> 00:21:06.830
Every cell and every

00:21:06.840 --> 00:21:09.350
hair on our head

00:21:09.360 --> 00:21:11.269
was

00:21:11.279 --> 00:21:14.510
fearfully and wonderfully

00:21:14.520 --> 00:21:16.950
made.

00:21:16.950 --> 00:21:16.960
I

00:21:16.960 --> 00:21:20.669
thank

00:21:20.679 --> 00:21:23.430
You

00:21:23.430 --> 00:21:23.440
that

00:21:23.440 --> 00:21:25.630
we

00:21:25.640 --> 00:21:28.149
go up higher and higher

00:21:28.159 --> 00:21:31.149
with You in greater

00:21:31.159 --> 00:21:34.269
glory and greater manifestations of Your

00:21:34.279 --> 00:21:36.789
presence.

00:21:40.360 --> 00:21:42.870
We want to be at

00:21:42.880 --> 00:21:46.310
the spout where the glory comes out,

00:21:46.320 --> 00:21:49.549
going from glory to glory. I thank You, Lord, for the manifestations of that glory

00:21:50.679 --> 00:21:53.430
in

00:21:56.000 --> 00:21:59.350
our homes. We

00:21:59.350 --> 00:21:59.360
want to

00:21:59.360 --> 00:22:01.669
be a

00:22:01.679 --> 00:22:09.430
vessel that You use in these last

00:22:09.440 --> 00:22:12.110
days. The eyes of the Lord

00:22:12.110 --> 00:22:12.120
run

00:22:12.120 --> 00:22:13.990
to and fro throughout the

00:22:14.000 --> 00:22:16.630
whole earth, looking for a heart whose

00:22:16.630 --> 00:22:16.640
heart is

00:22:16.640 --> 00:22:18.470
perfect toward

00:22:18.470 --> 00:22:18.480
Him.

00:22:18.480 --> 00:22:22.870
Let Your eyes rest upon me today, oh

00:22:22.880 --> 00:22:27.029
God.

00:22:32.120 --> 00:22:36.110
Create in me a clean heart, oh

00:22:36.120 --> 00:22:39.590
God. You

00:22:39.600 --> 00:22:43.549
are the Potter and I am the clay; mold me

00:22:43.559 --> 00:22:46.590
and make me today. We have this

00:22:46.600 --> 00:22:48.310
treasure in earthen vessels, that the

00:22:48.320 --> 00:22:50.750
excellency of the power would be of

00:22:50.760 --> 00:23:04.070
You and not of me.

00:23:04.080 --> 00:23:06.510
Holy

00:23:06.520 --> 00:23:11.029
Spirit, make me more like

00:23:11.039 --> 00:23:13.269
Jesus.

00:23:16.240 --> 00:23:19.789
We are yielded, filled,

00:23:19.789 --> 00:23:19.799
and

00:23:19.799 --> 00:23:23.310
controlled by the Holy Spirit

00:23:23.320 --> 00:23:26.990
today.

00:23:29.600 --> 00:23:32.950
We are at that

00:23:32.960 --> 00:23:35.190
river of living water flowing out of

00:23:35.190 --> 00:23:35.200
the

00:23:35.200 --> 00:23:38.590
throne.

00:23:38.600 --> 00:23:41.230
We're coming

00:23:41.240 --> 00:23:43.909
up higher with the fire. There are levels

00:23:43.919 --> 00:23:45.669
of the prophetic

00:23:45.669 --> 00:23:45.679
and

00:23:45.679 --> 00:23:48.149
levels of Your presence. Father, we yield

00:23:48.149 --> 00:23:48.159
ourselves to You today

00:23:48.159 --> 00:23:50.669
so

00:24:00.120 --> 00:24:02.070
that we would be a light in the

00:24:02.080 --> 00:24:06.630
darkness and the salt of

00:24:06.630 --> 00:24:06.640
the earth—the

00:24:06.640 --> 00:24:09.350
salt

00:24:09.360 --> 00:24:12.029
that makes people thirsty

00:24:16.679 --> 00:24:18.909
for

00:24:22.039 --> 00:24:25.230
You.

00:24:29.159 --> 00:24:31.750
Help us to be the light to

00:24:31.760 --> 00:24:34.710
somebody today, an answer to prayer in

00:24:34.720 --> 00:24:36.149
their heart.

00:24:39.760 --> 00:24:43.789
Let Your glory shine on our

00:24:43.789 --> 00:24:43.799
faces

00:24:43.799 --> 00:24:45.510
like it did upon

00:24:45.520 --> 00:24:48.549
Moses. Let our

00:24:48.559 --> 00:24:52.149
shadow pass by like it did the disciples, so

00:24:52.149 --> 00:24:52.159
that

00:24:52.159 --> 00:24:54.350
healing

00:24:54.350 --> 00:24:54.360
flows.

00:24:54.360 --> 00:24:56.510
Even if they touched the

00:24:56.520 --> 00:24:58.950
shadow, the glory was

00:24:58.960 --> 00:25:02.510
pouring out so strong that

00:25:02.510 --> 00:25:02.520
it

00:25:02.520 --> 00:25:05.549
would heal them.

00:25:11.840 --> 00:25:15.950
Do it again, Lord! Do it

00:25:15.960 --> 00:25:21.590
in us; do it in me.

00:25:21.600 --> 00:25:25.350
Create in us a clean heart,

00:25:25.360 --> 00:25:29.710
God. In these last days, pour out Your

00:25:29.720 --> 00:25:33.110
Spirit upon us one more

00:25:33.120 --> 00:25:36.990
time like You did at Azusa Street.

00:25:49.360 --> 00:25:51.830
I thank You, Lord, for the

00:25:51.840 --> 00:25:54.590
greatest harvest of souls this world has

00:25:54.600 --> 00:25:57.350
ever seen—a

00:25:57.350 --> 00:25:57.360
billion-soul

00:25:57.360 --> 00:26:00.310
harvest

00:26:00.310 --> 00:26:00.320
that

00:26:00.320 --> 00:26:03.190
would happen quickly and

00:26:03.200 --> 00:26:06.350
suddenly in the name of Jesus.

00:26:37.240 --> 00:26:39.630
I call each

00:26:39.640 --> 00:26:41.269
person

00:26:41.279 --> 00:26:43.190
watching this video today healed and

00:26:43.200 --> 00:26:46.430
whole.

00:26:46.440 --> 00:26:48.269
Nothing is too big for You, Lord.

00:26:50.880 --> 00:26:54.470
I call them blessed, healed, and whole

00:26:57.520 --> 00:27:00.230
mentally, emotionally,

00:27:00.240 --> 00:27:06.789
physically, and financially.

00:27:06.799 --> 00:27:10.310
I thank You, Father, for healing

00:27:10.320 --> 00:27:12.909
power that flows on the inside of them,

00:27:12.919 --> 00:27:16.630
driving out all sickness

00:27:16.630 --> 00:27:16.640
and

00:27:16.640 --> 00:27:19.710
disease.

00:27:22.120 --> 00:27:25.230
It's already done, and we receive it.

00:27:25.240 --> 00:27:27.149
Faith calls those things that be not as

00:27:27.159 --> 00:27:29.590
though they were.

00:27:29.600 --> 00:27:32.029
You paid the

00:27:32.039 --> 00:27:35.110
price for us to

00:27:35.120 --> 00:27:38.669
walk in

00:27:38.679 --> 00:27:43.070
healing. Lord, we pray over our

00:27:43.080 --> 00:27:45.230
finances. You

00:27:45.240 --> 00:27:47.190
said to seek first the kingdom and all

00:27:47.200 --> 00:27:50.149
these things will be added.

00:27:50.159 --> 00:27:51.789
We seek You today,

00:27:51.789 --> 00:27:51.799
knowing

00:27:51.799 --> 00:27:53.590
You know we have every

00:27:53.600 --> 00:27:56.630
need. We

00:28:08.919 --> 00:28:12.509
seek You, not

00:28:12.519 --> 00:28:17.310
for the things, but

00:28:21.470 --> 00:28:21.480
for

00:28:24.919 --> 00:28:26.230
You.

00:28:32.720 --> 00:28:34.710
We take the care out of our prayer

00:28:34.710 --> 00:28:34.720
and

00:28:34.720 --> 00:28:37.230
cast our cares onto You because

00:28:37.240 --> 00:28:40.070
You care for us. If You care for

00:28:40.080 --> 00:28:41.870
the lily of the field and

00:28:41.880 --> 00:28:43.750
the sparrow, how much more do You care

00:28:43.760 --> 00:28:44.870
for us?

00:28:44.880 --> 00:28:48.110
David

00:28:48.120 --> 00:28:51.269
said he

00:28:51.269 --> 00:28:51.279
had

00:28:51.279 --> 00:28:54.230
never seen the righteous forsaken nor

00:28:54.230 --> 00:28:54.240
his

00:28:54.240 --> 00:28:57.669
seed begging bread.

00:28:57.679 --> 00:29:00.789
I thank

00:29:00.799 --> 00:29:03.029
You that we are the

00:29:03.039 --> 00:29:06.149
righteousness of God in Christ Jesus.

00:29:12.320 --> 00:29:15.630
As we seek You daily,

00:29:15.640 --> 00:29:18.750
we will find

00:29:18.760 --> 00:29:21.230
You. We knock, and the door is

00:29:21.230 --> 00:29:21.240
opened

00:29:21.240 --> 00:29:23.350
to

00:29:23.360 --> 00:29:26.310
us.

00:29:26.320 --> 00:29:28.830
You have

00:29:28.840 --> 00:29:31.470
prepared

00:29:31.480 --> 00:29:35.230
a table before

00:29:35.230 --> 00:29:35.240
us

00:29:35.240 --> 00:29:37.430
in the presence of

00:29:42.279 --> 00:29:44.630
our enemies, and

00:29:44.630 --> 00:29:44.640
we rest

00:29:44.640 --> 00:29:47.230
in the finished work of Jesus

00:29:47.240 --> 00:29:50.549
Christ.

00:30:02.120 --> 00:30:05.990
Great is Your faithfulness

00:30:06.000 --> 00:30:09.509
to

00:30:11.799 --> 00:30:16.110
us.

00:30:23.559 --> 00:30:26.110
Morning by

00:30:26.120 --> 00:30:31.149
morning, new mercies I

00:30:31.159 --> 00:30:34.630
see; all I have

00:30:34.640 --> 00:30:39.830
needed Thy hand

00:30:39.830 --> 00:30:39.840
hath

00:30:39.840 --> 00:30:44.070
provided.

00:30:58.639 --> 00:31:01.789
Thank

00:31:20.600 --> 00:31:23.789
You

00:31:32.440 --> 00:31:34.389
for our unsaved loved ones.

00:31:34.399 --> 00:31:37.110
We send

00:31:37.110 --> 00:31:37.120
laborers

00:31:37.120 --> 00:31:39.430
across their path today.

00:31:43.200 --> 00:31:46.509
Some plant, some water, and

00:31:46.519 --> 00:31:49.310
some bring forth the increase, but we

00:31:49.320 --> 00:31:52.470
keep the door open by the blood.

00:32:09.120 --> 00:32:13.590
We call them home in Jesus'name. One last call—wake up! We

00:32:13.600 --> 00:32:17.149
call them to a fresh touch from

00:32:17.159 --> 00:32:19.509
Jesus.

00:32:40.760 --> 00:32:43.310
Now, I'm going to pray in

00:32:43.320 --> 00:32:46.070
tongues

00:32:46.070 --> 00:32:46.080
and

00:32:46.080 --> 00:32:48.230
pray perfect prayers out

00:32:48.240 --> 00:32:50.509
of my spirit.

00:32:52.639 --> 00:32:54.750
I

00:33:00.190 --> 00:33:00.200
thank

00:33:05.399 --> 00:33:08.070
You, Holy Spirit,

00:33:08.080 --> 00:33:10.230
that You move

00:33:10.240 --> 00:33:13.149
in me and

00:33:13.149 --> 00:33:13.159
pray

00:33:13.159 --> 00:33:15.070
perfect prayers that

00:33:15.070 --> 00:33:15.080
go

00:33:15.080 --> 00:33:16.909
straight to the throne.

00:33:21.350 --> 00:33:56.710
I'm

00:34:26.720 --> 00:34:31.570
interceding

00:35:15.079 --> 00:35:17.150
now

00:35:17.160 --> 00:35:18.990
over that virus

00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:20.470
they were talking

00:35:20.480 --> 00:35:23.390
about,

00:35:27.160 --> 00:35:29.510
calling

00:35:29.520 --> 00:35:32.750
forth divine protection over the

00:35:32.760 --> 00:35:35.589
righteous.

00:36:29.839 --> 00:36:33.550
I'm seeing a

00:36:33.550 --> 00:36:33.560
wristwatch,

00:36:33.560 --> 00:36:39.070
a clock that is going backwards,

00:37:06.400 --> 00:37:09.430
rewinding and giving more time.

00:38:55.920 --> 00:39:00.630
Time is running

00:39:00.640 --> 00:39:03.349
out.

00:42:52.760 --> 00:42:55.510
The hand of time is

00:42:55.520 --> 00:42:59.190
coming to an end for this

00:42:59.200 --> 00:43:01.309
dispensation. We are getting

00:43:01.319 --> 00:43:03.829
ready to step into the Millennial

00:43:03.839 --> 00:43:05.950
Reign.

00:43:13.599 --> 00:43:15.150
When You showed me the wristwatch

00:43:15.150 --> 00:43:15.160
and

00:43:15.160 --> 00:43:16.750
Trump, I

00:43:16.760 --> 00:43:21.390
wondered

00:43:21.400 --> 00:43:25.109
if

00:43:25.119 --> 00:43:28.030
we need to lift him

00:43:28.030 --> 00:43:28.040
up—that

00:43:28.040 --> 00:43:32.030
his time is not over.

00:43:32.040 --> 00:43:35.069
Father, bring in one

00:43:35.079 --> 00:43:39.510
final push,

00:43:39.520 --> 00:43:42.549
waking up the bride

00:43:42.549 --> 00:43:42.559
and

00:43:42.559 --> 00:43:44.670
the church.

00:43:44.680 --> 00:43:46.950
We don't look to

00:43:46.960 --> 00:43:51.309
a man to save this nation; we look to

00:43:51.319 --> 00:43:54.510
Jesus. It will only

00:43:54.520 --> 00:44:00.990
be an awakening unto God that will save

00:44:01.000 --> 00:44:03.150
America. I

00:44:06.000 --> 00:44:08.510
pray a special

00:44:08.520 --> 00:44:11.309
covering over every individual

00:44:11.319 --> 00:44:14.150
here, that the plague does not come nigh

00:44:14.160 --> 00:44:17.069
us. No virus in hell

00:44:17.079 --> 00:44:20.390
can come nigh us. We cover ourselves

00:44:20.390 --> 00:44:20.400
and

00:44:20.400 --> 00:44:23.470
our families in the blood.

00:44:23.480 --> 00:44:25.030
We

00:44:36.559 --> 00:44:40.109
are in the peace that passes all

00:44:40.119 --> 00:44:42.870
understanding

00:44:45.000 --> 00:44:48.069
concerning our hearts

00:44:48.069 --> 00:44:48.079
and

00:44:48.079 --> 00:44:50.270
families. We thank You, Lord, that we're

00:44:50.280 --> 00:44:55.349
always in the right place at the right

00:44:55.359 --> 00:44:58.109
time.

00:51:17.839 --> 00:51:20.150
Thank you for

00:51:20.160 --> 00:51:22.150
joining me today.

00:51:24.359 --> 00:51:26.630
I know a lot of you have to get back

00:51:26.640 --> 00:51:29.109
to work, but I

00:51:29.119 --> 00:51:31.270
wanted to give a little video of

00:51:31.280 --> 00:51:33.630
prayer so you could

00:51:33.640 --> 00:51:36.549
jump in the river and

00:51:36.549 --> 00:51:36.559
get

00:51:36.559 --> 00:51:41.270
some

00:51:41.280 --> 00:51:43.470
encouragement on the way to work.

00:51:45.720 --> 00:51:48.670
If you liked it, give it a thumbs

00:51:48.680 --> 00:51:51.829
up. I'll do more like this if

00:51:51.839 --> 00:51:54.750
you want to sing or pray more

00:51:54.760 --> 00:51:57.589
with me. It's on my

00:51:57.599 --> 00:51:59.829
heart. I want to pray more about the

00:51:59.839 --> 00:52:01.549
thing I just saw: Trump's face and

00:52:01.559 --> 00:52:04.190
that clock. It was a

00:52:04.200 --> 00:52:07.630
wristwatch

00:52:07.640 --> 00:52:09.150
moving backwards and then

00:52:09.160 --> 00:52:11.069
forwards

00:52:11.079 --> 00:52:12.829
to the 15-minute mark. It was a short span of time—a delay, but then it

00:52:12.839 --> 00:52:14.750
moved back.

00:52:31.839 --> 00:52:34.109
It's like

00:52:34.119 --> 00:52:37.150
He's saying time's up; He gave more

00:52:37.160 --> 00:52:41.069
time, and now the time is

00:52:41.079 --> 00:52:45.589
up. Jesus is coming, folks, and

00:52:45.599 --> 00:52:48.750
I hope you all are ready. We are

00:52:48.760 --> 00:52:51.990
going to see a great harvest of souls.

00:52:52.000 --> 00:52:55.150
There is

00:52:55.160 --> 00:52:58.069
going to be a move of His presence

00:52:58.079 --> 00:53:00.950
beyond anybody's comprehension. It

00:53:00.960 --> 00:53:04.190
will be

00:53:04.190 --> 00:53:04.200
a

00:53:04.200 --> 00:53:08.150
quick work.

00:53:08.150 --> 00:53:08.160
Then

00:53:08.160 --> 00:53:09.710
we'll

00:53:16.760 --> 00:53:18.270
be

00:53:18.280 --> 00:53:19.829
caught up

00:53:19.829 --> 00:53:19.839
for

00:53:19.839 --> 00:53:22.789
the

00:53:22.789 --> 00:53:22.799
seven-year

00:53:22.799 --> 00:53:24.870
tribulation to be with Him, and then

00:53:24.880 --> 00:53:26.870
we'll come back down.

00:53:29.440 --> 00:53:32.190
I want you all to be encouraged today.

00:53:32.200 --> 00:53:34.630
Yes, there are dark days, but the light

00:53:34.640 --> 00:53:37.309
is getting lighter.

00:53:37.319 --> 00:53:39.109
You have

00:53:39.119 --> 00:53:40.870
authority and are seated with Him in

00:53:40.880 --> 00:53:42.589
the heavenlies. You have

00:53:42.599 --> 00:53:44.870
nothing to fear as a believer

00:53:44.880 --> 00:53:47.190
bought with the blood of Jesus.

00:53:47.200 --> 00:53:49.309
To be absent from the body is to

00:53:49.319 --> 00:53:52.910
be present with the Lord.

00:53:57.880 --> 00:54:00.109
When we die, we go home to

00:54:00.109 --> 00:54:00.119
see

00:54:00.119 --> 00:54:02.030
Jesus; we're instantaneously with Him in

00:54:02.040 --> 00:54:04.390
glory.

00:54:04.400 --> 00:54:07.270
Jesus has a plan

00:54:07.280 --> 00:54:10.990
for your life to prosper

00:54:11.000 --> 00:54:13.230
you and be in health, even as your soul

00:54:13.240 --> 00:54:15.789
prospers. There

00:54:15.789 --> 00:54:15.799
are

00:54:15.799 --> 00:54:18.829
good days ahead for the believers.

00:54:22.680 --> 00:54:24.630
If

00:54:24.640 --> 00:54:25.990
you're new here

00:54:25.990 --> 00:54:26.000
and

00:54:26.000 --> 00:54:27.630
never seen

00:54:27.640 --> 00:54:30.270
me before, God bless you for sticking

00:54:30.280 --> 00:54:33.069
around.

00:54:34.960 --> 00:54:37.230
I'm

00:54:37.240 --> 00:54:38.670
going to do more videos like this

00:54:38.680 --> 00:54:40.750
because the Lord told me to.

00:54:40.760 --> 00:54:43.309
Put a smile on your face and a song

00:54:43.319 --> 00:54:46.109
in your heart. Jesus loves you so much.

00:54:46.119 --> 00:54:48.510
God bless you and have a

00:54:48.520 --> 00:54:50.670
wonderful day. See you next

00:54:50.680 --> 00:54:54.240
time.

